@heading Manpage Colors

@defvr {Setting} less_termcap_color
This master switch will make @b{BashStyle-NG} adjust the colors of manpages and
enforce the variable $PAGER to be set to @code{less} for this to work.
@end defvr

The following settings allow to customize the different parts of manapges, using
@b{Bashstyle-NG}'s predefinied colors.
